{
  "stem": "21978.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we have been told later, from archives and from news, there have been-- my father died soon after they were in Lodz, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother was working in a straw factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were making shoes-- covers for the shoes for the soldiers-- for German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know how much she suffered by it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What my little sister did, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I always hoped that she was [INAUDIBLE] when she was taken away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was in '41.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In '45, she would have been a teenager.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I hoped that she might have survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I hoped that one day we will see her, some day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I remember we were walking through the streets of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[CRYING] There was a young girl, [SOBBING] and we called her-- called to her, Lizinka!",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because that was the nickname.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[CRYING] It was not her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, eventually I found out, also, that my husband didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were-- there were survivors who told us that he didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Where was he, and that he didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Somebody told me he took his own life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Somebody told me he threw himself on the-- on the electrified barb-- barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We have found friends-- Christian friends-- who were very good to us, who took us in their house like a family.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We knew them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were friends from our family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The husband was Ger-- was Jewish, and he was in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But his wife was not, and he was-- she was supporting him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We called them mother and father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But we were adults.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We were 21 already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we have decided that we will do something with our lives.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
